    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "That's a good start, very dramatic. Can you make it a bit more specific to the people they're seeing? Like, describe how they look and act compared to the crew, and maybe have the explorer talk more about why they are inherently incapable of governing themselves without this 'civilizing' mission. Really lean into that 19th-century perspective on their intellect and social structure.",
